{"paging":{"is_end":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/565979950/child_comments?include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=5\u0026tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/565979950/child_comments?include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026include=%24%5B%2A%5D.author%2Creply_to_author%2Ccontent%2Cvote_count\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=3\u0026tdsourcetag=s_pctim_aiomsg","totals":21},"data":[{"id":566019932,"type":"comment","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/comments/566019932","vote_count":14,"voting":false,"created_time":1545831192,"is_delete":false,"resource_type":"answer","content":"\u003cp\u003e我对你无语了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e论难度，西塔潘猜想跟哥德巴赫猜想猜想比起来，你大概可以类比你的个人资产和万达、腾讯、阿里巴巴、苹果、微软、英特尔、AMD、三星……你能叫得出名字的大公司的资产总和。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e西塔潘猜想能被一名中南大学的学生证明出来，这是一个大新闻，值得报道，但是这是可以理解的，是一个具有很高天赋的学生通过努力（也许还有灵感）能够做到的，不是神迹。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想能被一个连大学数学都没学过的高中生证明出来，这个事儿发生的概率大概还比不上上帝突然降临在川普面前然后扇了他一巴掌的概率大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这两件事完全没有类比的可能。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个穷人也许可以通过自我奋斗和历史的行程成为亿万富翁，甚至登顶福布斯财富榜；但是你觉得他能从身无分文花费一年就收购万达、腾讯、阿里巴巴、苹果、微软、英特尔、AMD、三星……以及其它所有你能叫得出名字的大公司么？你以为现实是网络小说？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不要妄想了。世界不是绕着某个人转的，像伟大领袖那样开挂的人一千年可能都出不了一个，更何况我们在讨论的可能性开的挂比伟大领袖的挂还大。\u003c/p\u003e","author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"b71ffeb959ae94d30b0d5bdcf85c46f5","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/b71ffeb959ae94d30b0d5bdcf85c46f5","name":"白书旭","headline":"失学儿童","gender":1,"avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/8fcfdf2519a5ef8ca5194dc35551dbb7_s.jpg","type":"people","user_type":"people","badge":[],"is_following":false,"is_followed":false}},"is_author":false,"allow_like":true,"allow_delete":false,"replies_count":0,"can_recommend":false,"can_collapse":false,"reply_to_author":{"role":"normal","member":{"id":"56f29b56e54fd041c755b08668159d82","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/56